defaultNurseryman
defaultTree Surgeon
defaultDirector of an explosive company
default&#xa0;
defaultAll the above have the potential to cause harm to others so, even if they are not undertakings of a prescribed description, they would not be exempt from the law because of the provision indefault&#xa0;default&#xa0;defaults3(2A)(b) above. In otherdefault&#xa0;default&#xa0;defaultwords the duty can still apply if not on the prescribed listdefault. For clarity purposes the Government
default&#xa0;
